      "rationale": "Experimental validation tests were conducted using the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry with bovine blood at 37 °C, matching the COU fluid properties. Flow rates (2–8 L/min) and rotational speeds (2500–3500 rpm) span the intended VAD operating envelope. Test conditions are documented and traceable to calibrated instrumentation records.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
