      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison of CFD-predicted hemolysis index against experimental measurements uses the validation metric of mean absolute relative error (MARE = 8.3%) with expanded uncertainty bounds from Monte Carlo UQ. All predictions fall within experimental uncertainty bands. Comparison methodology follows ASME V&V 20 procedures.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
