        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "MARE < 15% for hemolysis index across all five operating points; CFD predictions must fall within combined experimental and model uncertainty bands at 95% confidence. Comparison must follow ASME V&V 20 quantitative validation metric."
