      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "The primary QoI — normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) — is identical in the validation experiment and the COU. Secondary QoIs (shear stress distribution, residence time) are also compared. No QoI translation or surrogate mapping is required.",
