      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) is the established form for CFD hemolysis prediction; its applicability to the VAD flow regime is supported by the validation evidence. Turbulence closure (SST k-ω) is justified by sensitivity analysis showing < 3% QoI variation relative to RSM closure at the operating points of interest.",
